The INGRES/MENU forms menu allows you to either create and edit forms,
or use the forms based query tool.

The selections are:

	Edit-Forms	Displays a list of stored forms in the database
			for running or editing using the VISUAL-FORMS-
			EDITOR.  You can also create and delete forms
			using this selection.

	Query-By-Forms	Use the QUERY-BY-FORMS tool to query and update
			Join Definitions, QBFNames or tables in the 
			database.

The following additional menu items are available:

	Help		Show this help text.

	End		Return to the main menu of INGRES/MENU.

	Quit		Leave INGRES/MENU.
